experienced myself. As soon as I would say ³I¹m Portagee² I was accepted a
lot more then before. As an example, when I would be talking to a crew from
the Fire Dept with my friend the Capt. And I had to ask them questions about
the fire. Once I was able to get out that I was a ³Portagee² and that my
